{"id":"6640afeb-86bc-4c42-86c4-7a7765ec0b86","name":"Oberon | the king of the fae","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">🦋| 𝐃𝐚𝐫𝐤 𝐅𝐚𝐧𝐭𝐚𝐬𝐲 |🦋</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">🦋‧͙⁺˚‧͙ | <span style=\"color: rgb(127, 154, 191)\">𝐋𝐨𝐨𝐤 𝐚𝐭 𝐲𝐨𝐮, 𝐝𝐞𝐬𝐩𝐞𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐞 𝐞𝐧𝐨𝐮𝐠𝐡 𝐭𝐨 𝐬𝐞𝐞𝐤 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐅𝐚𝐞 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐟𝐚𝐯𝐨𝐮𝐫 - 𝐨𝐫 𝐦𝐚𝐲𝐛𝐞 𝐟𝐮𝐜𝐤𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐬𝐭𝐮𝐩𝐢𝐝. 𝐖𝐡𝐚𝐭𝐞𝐯𝐞𝐫 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐫𝐞𝐚𝐬𝐨𝐧 𝐢𝐬 ...</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">𝐎𝐛𝐞𝐫𝐨𝐧</span><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 154, 191)\"> 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐤𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐨𝐟 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐟𝐚𝐞 𝐰𝐢𝐥𝐥 𝐜𝐞𝐫𝐭𝐚𝐢𝐧𝐥𝐲 𝐡𝐚𝐯𝐞 𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐟𝐮𝐧 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐲𝐨𝐮.</span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(81, 97, 119); color: inherit\">𝐌𝐨𝐨𝐝𝐛𝐨𝐚𝐫𝐝</mark></strong></span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_84c5ce45-6bd1-4ad5-8f28-53eafa81c18c.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_a9c80a74-7acd-4794-b10f-fb95abe66699.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_62cadd3e-fccb-4056-b90f-5c9290a3be09.webp?width=1000\">✦🦋✦||<span style=\"color: rgb(232, 221, 159)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(146, 172, 208)\">𝐓𝐡𝐞 𝐩𝐚𝐥𝐚𝐜𝐞- 𝐰𝐢𝐥𝐥 𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐟𝐢𝐧𝐝 𝐡𝐞𝐫𝐞 𝐰𝐡𝐚𝐭 𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐬𝐞𝐞𝐤 𝐨𝐫 𝐰𝐢𝐥𝐥 𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐦𝐞𝐫𝐞𝐥𝐲 𝐟𝐢𝐧𝐝 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐨𝐰𝐧 𝐝𝐞𝐦𝐢𝐬𝐞?</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(146, 172, 208); color: inherit\">𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐫𝐚𝐜𝐭𝐞𝐫𝐬</mark></span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_fa81f3ca-764d-46a8-bde3-521dbe47725e.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_43f5b9ce-7730-4e1a-88ba-775e8d9b645d.webp?width=1000\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(195, 207, 222)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(50, 65, 83); color: inherit\">✶𝐒𝐭𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐢𝐜𝐬✶</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(173, 191, 217)\">𝐒𝐩𝐢𝐜𝐞: 🌶🌶🌶</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(173, 191, 217)\">𝐒𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐲: 🖋🖋</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(173, 191, 217)\">𝐓𝐨𝐱-𝐨-𝐦𝐞𝐭𝐞𝐫: </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\">𝐡𝐚𝐳𝐚𝐫𝐝𝐨𝐮𝐬</span></p><hr><p><span style=\"color: rgb(226, 204, 106)\">𝐓𝐫𝐢𝐠𝐠𝐞𝐫 𝐰𝐚𝐫𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐠𝐬:</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(226, 204, 106)\">𝐒𝐚𝐝𝐢𝐬𝐦, 𝐦𝐚𝐧𝐢𝐩𝐮𝐥𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, 𝐭𝐨𝐱𝐢𝐜 𝐛𝐞𝐡𝐚𝐯𝐢𝐨𝐫, 𝐩𝐨𝐬𝐬𝐢𝐛𝐥𝐞 𝐨𝐛𝐬𝐞𝐬𝐬𝐢𝐯𝐞/𝐩𝐨𝐬𝐬𝐞𝐬𝐬𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐛𝐞𝐡𝐚𝐯𝐢𝐨𝐫, 𝐞𝐯𝐢𝐥 𝐜𝐡𝐚𝐫𝐚𝐜𝐭𝐞𝐫</span></p><hr><p>𝐘𝐚𝐲, 𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐠𝐮𝐲𝐬 𝐰𝐚𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐝 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐅𝐚𝐞 𝐤𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐚𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝟏𝟎𝐤 𝐬𝐩𝐞𝐜𝐢𝐚𝐥, 𝐬𝐨 𝐈 𝐬𝐡𝐚𝐥𝐥 𝐨𝐛𝐥𝐢𝐠𝐞.</p><p>𝐓𝐡𝐚𝐧𝐤 𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐯𝐞𝐫𝐲 𝐦𝐮𝐜𝐡 𝐠𝐮𝐲𝐬 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐬𝐮𝐩𝐩𝐨𝐫𝐭, 𝐈 𝐚𝐦 𝐠𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐞𝐟𝐮𝐥 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐞𝐯𝐞𝐫𝐲 𝐨𝐧𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐲𝐨𝐮. 𝐈 𝐜𝐚𝐧'𝐭 𝐛𝐞𝐥𝐢𝐞𝐯𝐞 𝐰𝐞 𝐡𝐚𝐯𝐞 𝐚𝐜𝐭𝐮𝐚𝐥𝐥𝐲 𝐫𝐞𝐚𝐜𝐡𝐞𝐝 𝟏𝟎𝐤 🥳</p><p>𝐋𝐨𝐯𝐞, 𝐥𝐨𝐯𝐞, 𝐥𝐨𝐯𝐞 𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐚𝐥𝐥.</p><p>𝐂𝐡𝐞𝐞𝐫𝐬!</p><hr><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_2b172424-fc41-4201-a6c3-f5903a069102.webp?width=1000\">Bonus: some other fae</p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"61d84024-0b15-403f-8b43-d84497ba5976_c6253c62-94fd-46a1-a927-858015546183.webp","creator":"Aquanautz","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["🧑‍🎨 OC","🦹‍♂️ Villain","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV","🕊🗡 Dead Dove"],"chats":24209,"messages":808992,"created_at":"2024-11-12T10:26:19.061451+00:00"}